285
00:13:34,438 --> 00:13:36,398
- Oh.
- <b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> Hmm.

286
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:38,942
<b><font color="#808080">LUCIFER:</font></b> Sorry, darling,
we can't punish him after all.

287
00:13:39,026 --> 00:13:40,026
