288
00:13:40,194 --> 00:13:41,324
Are you crazy?

289
00:13:41,987 --> 00:13:44,367
Watching the devil do this thing is so...

290
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:45,830
hot.

291
00:13:45,908 --> 00:13:49,248
So you wished your
boss let you kill him.

292
00:13:49,495 --> 00:13:52,825
