293
00:13:52,915 --> 00:13:54,285
Lawyer. Now.

294
00:14:01,507 --> 00:14:02,507
I mean...

295
00:14:02,925 --> 00:14:03,925
Turn around.

296
00:14:06,345 --> 00:14:07,345
<b><font color="#D900D9">[EVE SQUEALS]</font></b>

297
00:14:07,388 --> 00:14:08,548
<b><font color="#808080">LUCIFER:</font></b> It's fun, isn't it?

298
00:14:09,723 --> 00:14:10,723
<b><font color="#808080">ELLA:</font></b> Hey, Chloe.

299
00:14:12,184 --> 00:14:14,274
