that they get the corporate perks.

305
00:14:25,531 --> 00:14:28,081
Like covering their
gym membership fees.

306
00:14:28,367 --> 00:14:30,867
So who's paying for Pony Boy
to get so jacked?

307
00:14:30,953 --> 00:14:33,713
It looks like it all tracks back
to Jacob Tiernan here.

308
00:14:33,789 --> 00:14:35,169
That paralyzed dude's dad?

309
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,800
Does this have something
to do with that case?

310
