Tiernan's son shows up
paralyzed from the chest down.

311
00:14:40,462 --> 00:14:42,842
Then this guy dies.
So it has to be, right?

312
00:14:42,923 --> 00:14:45,803
I think Sam's bones were
broken before he was killed

313
00:14:45,885 --> 00:14:47,965
in the exact same spot
that Julian's was.

314
00:14:48,304 --> 00:14:49,514
Julian McCaffrey?

315
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:51,890
- <b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> Yeah.
- What does this have to do with him?

316
00:14:51,974 --> 00:14:54,444
Maybe Tiernan thought that
Sam broke Julian's back.

317
00:14:54,518 --> 00:14:56,558
Normally he'd hire Pony Boy
to do his dirty work,

318
00:14:56,645 --> 00:14:59,265
- but it's his son so...
- He wanted to enact revenge himself

319
00:14:59,356 --> 00:15:01,226
and borrowed Pony Boy's gun to do it.

320
00:15:01,317 --> 00:15:02,937
- Yes.
- I'll get you the ME report.

321
00:15:03,277 --> 00:15:04,277
Great.

322
00:15:08,032 --> 00:15:09,582
Hey. Luce.

323
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:10,700
I did that.

324
00:15:11,368 --> 00:15:14,498
I broke Julian's back.
Tiernan killed an innocent man.

325
00:15:15,539 --> 00:15:16,619
What does that mean?

326
00:15:17,875 --> 00:15:20,955
It means, my dear,
that now more than ever

327
00:15:21,045 --> 00:15:23,415
that monster needs to be punished.

328
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:28,430
<b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> Mr. Tiernan,
I don't know if you heard

329
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:30,430
but a drug dealer was
killed this morning.

330
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:32,473
What does that have to do with me?

331
00:15:33,599 --> 00:15:35,939
<b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> Well, that's the interesting part.

332
00:15:36,018 --> 00:15:39,608
He had the exact same
spinal injury as your son.

333
00:15:39,897 --> 00:15:43,437
So it would seem that possibly
someone is out for revenge.

334
00:15:43,609 --> 00:15:46,279
My son worked with
a lot of bad people.

335
00:15:46,362 --> 00:15:49,202
In fact, Julian wasn't exactly
a good person himself,

336
00:15:49,281 --> 00:15:52,621
which is why I had to
excise him from my business.

337
00:15:53,202 --> 00:15:56,622
You... you love your children,
but at a certain point

338
00:15:56,705 --> 00:15:59,075
- you have to let them...
- Stand on their own two legs.

339
00:16:00,417 --> 00:16:03,457
<b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> Mr Tiernan, do you know a man
named Greg Grabowski?

340
00:16:04,672 --> 00:16:07,092
Goes by the colorful moniker "Pony Boy".

341
00:16:07,633 --> 00:16:08,633
No.

342
00:16:09,635 --> 00:16:10,885
<b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> Hmm. That's odd,

343
00:16:10,970 --> 00:16:13,350
because one of your
companies pays his bills.

344
00:16:13,764 --> 00:16:16,394
I have a lot of companies paying
a lot of people a lot of money.

345
00:16:16,475 --> 00:16:17,845
I don't keep track of every penny.

346
00:16:18,352 --> 00:16:20,692
You kept track of your
son, though, didn't you?

347
00:16:20,854 --> 00:16:23,574
Which is why you consistently
bailed him out of jail.

348
00:16:23,649 --> 00:16:25,779
Always getting him out of trouble.

349
00:16:26,402 --> 00:16:27,742
He never learned, did he?

350
00:16:27,987 --> 00:16:32,987
In fact, some might say it's your fault
he became a killer, a human trafficker.

351
00:16:33,826 --> 00:16:35,036
A broken little doll.

352
00:16:36,537 --> 00:16:37,537
<b><font color="#D900D9">[BANG]</font></b>

353
00:16:38,872 --> 00:16:40,792
My son had a lot of friends.

354
00:16:41,125 --> 00:16:45,625
Maybe one of them decided to make the
piece of garbage who crippled him pay.

355
00:16:45,963 --> 00:16:46,963
Really?

356
00:16:47,756 --> 00:16:49,796
Because I had a little chat with Julian

357
00:16:49,883 --> 00:16:52,303
right before he shot a
police officer in cold blood.

358
00:16:52,386 --> 00:16:55,636
He said that you were an even
worse person than he was.

359
00:16:56,181 --> 00:16:59,691
Mm. That must make you a true monster.

360
00:16:59,768 --> 00:17:02,518
Unless you have actual cause
to charge me with something,

361
00:17:02,604 --> 00:17:03,734
