368
00:17:19,538 --> 00:17:22,038
<b><font color="#D900D9">[CREAKING]</font></b>

369
00:17:22,124 --> 00:17:24,754
Lucifer. Lucifer, stop.

370
00:17:25,335 --> 00:17:27,545
Lucifer, do it.

371
00:17:27,629 --> 00:17:28,629
Get out!

372
00:17:28,964 --> 00:17:30,014
Detective...

373
00:17:30,591 --> 00:17:31,631
leave.

374
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:33,760
Stop.

375
00:17:37,639 --> 00:17:38,639
<b><font color="#D900D9">[COUGHS]</font></b>

376
00:17:40,059 --> 00:17:41,059
This isn't over.

377
00:17:55,199 --> 00:17:57,239
<b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> Tiernan killed Sam,
but we have no proof.

378
00:17:57,326 --> 00:17:58,156
So?

379
00:17:58,243 --> 00:18:00,373
So Tiernan's gonna
double his legal defense

380
00:18:00,454 --> 00:18:02,624
now that you've hulked out in his office.

