384
00:18:10,172 --> 00:18:11,632
Or Tiernan posted it for him.

385
00:18:11,882 --> 00:18:15,342
You're saying that we don't
get to punish anybody?

386
00:18:16,845 --> 00:18:18,635
Honey... you promised.

387
00:18:18,722 --> 00:18:20,122
Can we... give us a moment.
Thanks.

388
00:18:22,059 --> 00:18:23,539
<b><font color="#808080">CHLOE:</font></b> What the hell is up with you?

389
00:18:23,602 --> 00:18:25,312
I finally figured out who I am,
that's all.

390
00:18:25,813 --> 00:18:28,323
Lucifer,
this is not who you are.

391
00:18:29,149 --> 00:18:31,029
I think Eve is a bad influence on you.

392
00:18:32,027 --> 00:18:33,987
This has nothing to do with her.

393
00:18:34,071 --> 00:18:36,661
It's who I am, I punish people.

394
00:18:36,824 --> 00:18:41,204
So do I, but like I said, there is
a right way and there is a wrong way.

395
00:18:41,286 --> 00:18:43,406
What makes you the authority
on right and wrong?

396
00:18:43,539 --> 00:18:45,869
I'm a cop and it's the law.

397
00:18:45,958 --> 00:18:47,578
Well, I'm the devil. <b><font color="#D900D9">[CLAPS]</font></b>

398
00:18:49,002 --> 00:18:53,592
I ruled Hell. Bad people were sent to me
so they could get what they deserved.

399
00:18:53,757 --> 00:18:57,677
It is my job to do the same here
on Earth because when I don't...

400
00:19:01,306 --> 00:19:04,386
When I don't, bad things happen.

401
00:19:07,855 --> 00:19:10,515
That is why I broke Julian's back.

402
00:19:15,112 --> 00:19:18,202
And that is why I won't let
Tiernan get away with it.

403
00:19:19,616 --> 00:19:20,866
You broke Julian's back.

