do anything about it.

406
00:19:29,209 --> 00:19:30,209
Then why?

407
00:19:31,753 --> 00:19:34,803
Why ask me to leave
when we were in Tiernan's office?

408
00:19:34,882 --> 00:19:37,302
You were going to hurt him
and you wanted me to leave

409
00:19:37,467 --> 00:19:39,087
because you knew it was wrong.

410
00:19:39,261 --> 00:19:41,931
No. Because you've made it plainly clear

411
00:19:42,014 --> 00:19:44,184
