415
00:20:10,626 --> 00:20:11,626
Thank you, Margaret.

416
00:20:16,173 --> 00:20:17,933
He didn't just fall down that hill.

417
00:20:19,801 --> 00:20:21,721
Someone deliberately broke his back.

418
00:20:22,512 --> 00:20:23,642
And I know who it was.

419
00:20:24,973 --> 00:20:26,683
