420
00:20:26,767 --> 00:20:28,687
I don't have enough proof
to put him in jail...

421
00:20:29,228 --> 00:20:31,068
but he needs to be
accountable for his actions,

422
00:20:31,104 --> 00:20:32,524
and I know you're a powerful man...

423
00:20:34,024 --> 00:20:35,194
a man who ruins his enemies.

424
00:20:36,735 --> 00:20:37,735
I'm listening.

425
00:20:38,570 --> 00:20:39,570
Look.

426
00:20:41,990 --> 00:20:46,290
You could finally give him a taste
of the punishment he deserves.

427
00:20:47,287 --> 00:20:48,657
What is this man's name?

428
00:20:50,832 --> 00:20:52,082
Lucifer Morningstar.

429
00:20:58,048 --> 00:21:00,008
<b><font color="#808080">ELLA:</font></b> Since we know the
murder was personal,

430
00:21:00,092 --> 00:21:01,842
I looked back over the autopsy report

431
00:21:01,927 --> 00:21:05,387
and I was hoping we could find
spit or urine or something

432
00:21:05,472 --> 00:21:06,722
