435
00:21:10,519 --> 00:21:11,649
Do you get why?

436
00:21:12,187 --> 00:21:13,767
Anyway, no luck there,

437
00:21:13,855 --> 00:21:17,275
but I did notice that one
of his fingers was broken.

438
00:21:17,693 --> 00:21:19,783
